          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> tomatoes</strong> into wedges</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> ginger</strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>mango chutney</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
