      "instruction": "<p>Once the onions have softened, add the <strong>garam masala</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>ginger</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> tomato wedges</strong> and<strong> stock </strong>and give everything a good mix up - this is your <strong>vegetable rogan josh</strong></p>",
