      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>vegetable rogan josh</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven and cook for an initial 10-15 min or until the stock is starting to thicken and the<strong> </strong>tomatoes have softened</p>",
